column2: out1 <- estimate_all(data = ldw, Y = "re78", treat = "treat", cov = covar)

警告: Estimated treatment propensities take values between 0.003 and 0.988 and in particular get very close to 0 and 1. In this case, using `target.sample=overlap`, or filtering data as in Crump, Hotz, Imbens, and Mitnik (Biometrika, 2009) may be helpful.
